{"tid":2346352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英議員倡議簽訂英澳紐加自由行動協議","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T01:19:11.000Z","uid":305299,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ec00c6ba8578179b23c01180c95b91c6bb2601","tid":2346352,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n脫歐協議今日晏啲時間就會喺英國國會進行表決，保守黨下議院議員 Andrew Bridgen 接受澳洲傳媒訪問時表示，當脫歐協議正式獲國會通過後，佢希望英國政府可以集中火力同其他國家簽訂貿易協議，包括澳洲在內嘅 Canzuk (英澳紐加) 協議。佢希望見到四國嘅公民可以自由咁喺對方國家出入、工作或者創業。如果 Canzuk 得以落實，佢預計將會成為世界第四大經貿體。<br />\n<br />\nUK government MP pushes for 'free travel' trade bloc with Canada, Australia, NZ<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.skynews.com.au/details/_6219051232001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skynews.com.au%2Fdetails%2F_6219051232001&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSIGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=f65b94a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.skynews.com.au/details/_6219051232001</a>"},{"pid":"dcd1ad887667a16f71ce61e756a70e0b53a9cab7","tid":2346352,"uid":144626,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"呢招掂<br />\n五眼經濟圈<br />\n到時香港人拎左英籍就可以去呢堆國家經商或者定居<br />\n當然，大前提係踢走D支那人"},{"pid":"cbcf8a6fe6f0537a281bb7d2bcec257a2017c7b4","tid":2346352,"uid":307270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4c36d7a77ac928498c3c1e4a5fce3656ac7d1c","tid":2346352,"uid":30791,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"dcd1ad887667a16f71ce61e756a70e0b53a9cab7","tid":2346352,"uid":144626,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"呢招掂<br />\n五眼經濟圈<br />\n到時香港人拎左英籍就可以去呢堆國家經商或者定居<br />\n當然，大前提係踢走D支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\